name: FloatED-MOON (26) Favst
description:
Hello, my name is Edmoon Holeworld
Humans usually called me The Moon.
Eternal love, it's a thing that even death cannot perished it.
it's just a matter of how we translate it.
Bad or a good way, it's all the same coin.
As long as we or he is always remembered.
I hope I'm the one.
